window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Kelsey is a young recent college grad who's yearning to get her foot in the door and start the dream career she had always hoped for. She's stuck at a job she doesn't like, surrounded by people who don't appreciate her efforts. Her life is dull and nothing like she had imagined it would be by now. </p> <p>But fate has a way of colliding into us from angles unseen. When Kelsey runs into Brandon, everything changes. </p> <p>Brandon is an MMA fighter who became a billionaire before he was 30. His life is fast-paced and too full for him to have a moment to relax and enjoy his life. Kelsey is looking for something more in life, and Brandon is seeking for less of what his life now throws at him. </p> <p>Will the two of them find a middle ground, or are they both fighting a battle that can't be won? </p>"; 
